description: This file defines the `Vehicle` entity class for the backend of a taxi booking platform, representing vehicle details associated with drivers. It includes annotations for persistence and validation, as well as getters and setters for the entity's fields.

classes.name: Vehicle
classes.description: Entity class representing a vehicle with fields for ID, make, model, and plate number, including constructors and accessor methods.

methods.name: Vehicle
methods.description: Default constructor for the Vehicle entity.

methods.name: Vehicle
methods.description: Parameterized constructor initializing all fields of the Vehicle entity.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the unique identifier of the vehicle.

methods.name: setId
methods.description: Sets the unique identifier of the vehicle.

methods.name: getMake
methods.description: Returns the make (manufacturer) of the vehicle.

methods.name: setMake
methods.description: Sets the make (manufacturer) of the vehicle.

methods.name: getModel
methods.description: Returns the model of the vehicle.

methods.name: setModel
methods.description: Sets the model of the vehicle.

methods.name: getPlateNumber
methods.description: Returns the license plate number of the vehicle.

methods.name: setPlateNumber
methods.description: Sets the license plate number of the vehicle.
